    >12-15-2008</dc:date>
    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"
    >Articulation is the aspect of pronunciation that involves bringing articulatory organs together so as to shape the sounds of speech.</rdfs:comment>
